{"tid":2439227,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"足球壇有冇邊啲人係個「名」仲響過個「姓」？","createTime":"2021-03-09T05:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T09:36:06.000Z","uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0b0652af99c933eb7a985bd1ae1d8e9193efd481","tid":2439227,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"體壇最出名嘅例子應該係高比拜仁<br />\n你講Bryant 未必個個都第一時間諗起佢<br />\n但一講Kobe就知係邊個<br />\n<br />\n咁足球壇呢<br />\n係咪淨係得James Rodriguez<br />\n<br />\n名響過姓 應該真係冇乜可能<br />\n(政界同演藝界會多啲 因為通常都嗌全名)<br />\n但有冇邊啲人 係普通人都會知佢first name係咩?<br />\nDavid Beckham算唔算?"},{"pid":"68b4d904aebcb09c1ae6d2a11946d7a388f1d6a2","tid":2439227,"uid":165817,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:56:33.000Z","msg":"講起<span class=\"red\">姓</span>同<span class=\"gold\">名</span> 有啲想講下C朗同大爆<br />\n可能好多巴打都以為C朗<span class=\"red\">姓</span>朗拿度 大爆<span class=\"red\">姓</span>雷斯<br />\n其實「基斯坦奴朗拿度」同「大衛雷斯」先係個<span class=\"gold\">名</span><br />\n即係類似香港人嘅「Ka Chun」、「Wing Yan」<br />\n<br />\n佢地兩個個<span class=\"red\">姓</span>其實好少好少曝光<br />\n呢個應該係葡語系人嘅文化特色嚟<br />\n應該係因為全名太長 好多時都唔會理個<span class=\"red\">姓</span><br />\n將個<span class=\"gold\">名</span>當係全名咁用<br />\n<br />\n我都係N年前見到金球獎投票張form<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">First name</span>寫哂「Cristiano Ronaldo」而<span class=\"red\">second name</span>空咗<br />\n跟住先去研究下<br />\n發現其實好多葡語系球員都係咁 尤其是巴西人<br />\n例如羅拔圖費明奴 (Roberto Firmino)<br />\n門神祖利奧施薩 (Julio Cesar)<br />\n<br />\n當然都有例外<br />\n泰亞高施華就係由<span class=\"gold\">名</span>+<span class=\"red\">姓</span>組成<br />\nThiago係<span class=\"gold\">名</span>，Silva係<span class=\"red\">姓</span><br />\n加比爾捷西斯 Gabriel Jesus<br />\n仲有艾利臣碧加 Alisson Becker都係<span class=\"gold\">名</span>+<span class=\"red\">姓</span><br />\n<br />\n其他國家都有呢啲情況 不過少見好多<br />\n比較出名嘅例子應該係法卡奧 Radamel Falcao<br />\n應該好多人都以為法卡奧係<span class=\"red\">姓</span><br />\n其實Radamel Falcao全個係佢<span class=\"gold\">first name</span><br />\n佢係<span class=\"red\">姓</span>加西亞 Garcia"},{"pid":"248552386cd215951ea3dc10a40d2538b8ba5688","tid":2439227,"uid":195164,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:03:09.000Z","msg":"香港嗰d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806b26b276bc44824717788d2d25ea94660367bd","tid":2439227,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"248552386cd215951ea3dc10a40d2538b8ba5688","tid":2439227,"uid":195164,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:03:09.000Z","msg":"香港嗰d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />秒"},{"pid":"3a5a1505b2b27273aeeb936ecafde10bf80cdfd5","tid":2439227,"uid":68916,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:14:37.000Z","msg":"麥巴比？<br />\n個個都包皮包皮（巴比）咁叫<br />\n其實好少人知佢姓麥"},{"pid":"acb12d814db0141decb3803bef463f5c4e0519b7","tid":2439227,"uid":165817,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3a5a1505b2b27273aeeb936ecafde10bf80cdfd5","tid":2439227,"uid":68916,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:14:37.000Z","msg":"麥巴比？<br />\n個個都包皮包皮（巴比）咁叫<br />\n其實好少人知佢姓麥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"波台仲有創意過創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79244f1e8235bda1e7fa40a92b379ac094eecbc","tid":2439227,"uid":119695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:18:29.000Z","msg":"伯特、拉特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacaff0342e2582dc027c0e9bad623f2a7f6889a","tid":2439227,"uid":165817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a79244f1e82